U!But you have also stolen 100 hours of my life already... Are you proud?     I am sure you are ;)You’ve set new standards in the way a game should be delivered to the community and updated based on user feedback, and all gamers will benefit from your work.Kudos to everyone!!!Q: Where am I going?A: Sorry, I have a city to build... goodbye!"
